        <abstract>
            <p>Comments on CL’s advice not to reply directly to reviews.</p> 
<p>Describes work on his <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi> manuscript.</p>  
<p>Work delayed on his "larger book" [<hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>].</p>  
<p>Comments at length on the evolutionary significance of Robert McDonnell’s investigations ["On an organ in the skate", <hi rend="italic">Nat. Hist. Rev.</hi> (1861): 57–60].</p> 
        </abstract>
